$a = Real(random(2, 6, 1));
$a2 = $a**2;

$ans = Formula("(1 / $a) * asec(x / $a) + C");
$ans->{limits} = [$a,4*$a];

Context()->texStrings;
BEGIN_TEXT
\{ beginproblem() \}
\{ textbook_ref_exact("Rogawski ET 2e", "7.3","7") \}
$PAR
Use the substitution \( x = $a \sec t \) to evaluate the integral \( \int \frac{dx}{x\sqrt{x^2 - $a2}} \).
$PAR
\{ans_box( 3,60)\}
$PAR
Note: Use C for an arbitrary constant.
$PAR
END_TEXT
